---
source: tests/contracts/preflight_tripwires.rs
assertion: tripwire deeper checks evaluate persisted rules against explicit event payloads
schema:
  list: ee.tripwire.list.v1
  check: ee.tripwire.check.v1
  promotion: ee.tripwire.harm_promotion.v1
contracts:
  - empty stores return stable empty list output instead of an unavailable sentinel
  - missing tripwire IDs return not_found with tripwire_inputs_incomplete provenance
  - persisted event:<key.path>=<glob> rules match caller-supplied --event JSON
  - check events are logged with event payload hashes and mutation posture
  - harmful feedback at threshold proposes deterministic rule candidates
evidence:
  - tripwires.id
  - tripwires.condition
  - tripwire_check_events.event_payload_hash
  - tripwire_check_events.mutation_posture
  - curation_candidates.source_type
